Contributing To the Project
===========================

If you want to report a bug, use <https://plaimi.net/bugs>. If you want to 
discuss some more general things regarding the game, use 
<https://plaimi.net/forum>. If you want to contribute code, see HACKING for 
coding style guidelines, submission information and more. See TODO for 
information on what needs to be done. If you want to suggest a feature (i.e. 
you lack the skill/time to code it yourself), or have questions regarding 
anything, check the forum, or see AUTHORS for contact information.


